			  <p class="timeline-description">Leading a team of engineers in developing cutting-edge prototypes for various industries, focusing on IoT and AI integration. Responsible for full lifecycle from concept to validation.</p>
			  <div class="timeline-arrow"></div>
			</div>
			<div class="timeline-dot"></div>
		  </div>
   
		  <div class="timeline-item timeline-item-right">
			<div class="timeline-content">
			  <h3 class="timeline-title">Prototyping Engineer</h3>
			  <p class="timeline-company">Tech Solutions Inc.</p>
			  <p class="timeline-duration">Aug 2018 - Dec 2021</p>
			  <p class="timeline-description">Designed and built functional prototypes for consumer electronics, improving time-to-market by 20% through efficient iteration cycles.</p>
			  <div class="timeline-arrow"></div>
			</div>
			<div class="timeline-dot"></div>
		  </div>
   
		  <div class="timeline-item timeline-item-left">
			<div class="timeline-content">
			  <h3 class="timeline-title">Junior Hardware Developer</h3>
			  <p class="timeline-company">Circuit Innovations</p>
			  <p class="timeline-duration">May 2016 - Jul 2018</p>
			  <p class="timeline-description">Assisted in circuit board design and assembly for various electronic products, gaining hands-on experience in rapid prototyping techniques.</p>
			  <div class="timeline-arrow"></div>
			</div>
			<div class="timeline-dot"></div>
		  </div>
		</div>
	  </div>
